Class ShsMessageEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.inera.axel.shs.broker.messagestore.ShsMessageEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ShsMessageEntry
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Entity that represents an SHS message as routed in the broker and stored in the message log database.

    Contains the message header (label), id and state.
